    <resourceShortName lang="en">LanguageToolLemmatizer</resourceShortName>
    <resourceName lang="en">LanguageToolLemmatizer</resourceName>
    <description lang="en">Naive lexicon-based lemmatizer. The words are looked up using the wordform lexicons of
LanguageTool. Multiple readings are produced. The annotator simply takes the most frequent
lemma from those readings. If no readings could be found, the original text is assigned as
lemma.</description>
  </identificationInfo>
